    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/inventorygenentries-with-internalserialnumber/qaq-p/14053095</id>
    <title>InventoryGenEntries with InternalSerialNumber</title>
    <updated>2025-03-21T18:58:01.789000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>juanpmg2</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1486805</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;Good&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;afternoon&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;to&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;all&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;I&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;would&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;like&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;to&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;see&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;if&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;someone&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;can&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;help&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;me.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;I&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;can&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;successfully&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;enter&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;products&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;from&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;my&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;API&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;using&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;the&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN class=""&gt;endpoint&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://XXXXXX:50000/b1s/v1/InventoryGenEntries" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://XXXXXX:50000/b1s/v1/InventoryGenEntries&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;with the body&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;{&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"DocumentLines"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;: [&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; {&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"ItemCode"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"410224"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"Quantity"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"WarehouseCode"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"001"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"AccountCode"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;"1.01.004.01.002"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; }&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; ]&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;}&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;But now i need to send the lot number. I'm trying to do the following.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;{&lt;BR /&gt;"DocumentLines": [&lt;BR /&gt;{&lt;BR /&gt;"ItemCode": "410224",&lt;BR /&gt;"Quantity": 1,&lt;BR /&gt;"WarehouseCode": "001",&lt;BR /&gt;"AccountCode": "1.01.004.01.002",&lt;BR /&gt;"SerialNumbers": [&lt;BR /&gt;{&lt;BR /&gt;"InternalSerialNumber": "1424"&lt;BR /&gt;}&lt;BR /&gt;]&lt;BR /&gt;}&lt;BR /&gt;]&lt;BR /&gt;} but it give me this error&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;{&lt;BR /&gt;"error": {&lt;BR /&gt;"code": -10,&lt;BR /&gt;"message": {&lt;BR /&gt;"lang": "en-us",&lt;BR /&gt;"value": "10001172 - Blank strings are not allowed in row 1 (in unique field). [OSRN.SysNumber][line: 0]"&lt;BR /&gt;}&lt;BR /&gt;}&lt;BR /&gt;}. Can some one help me. Thank you!!!!&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/inventorygenentries-with-internalserialnumber/qaq-p/14053095"/>
    <published>2025-03-21T18:58:01.789000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/sap-b1-web-client-extension-not-showing/qaq-p/14055123</id>
    <title>SAP B1 Web Client Extension Not Showing</title>
    <updated>2025-03-24T19:50:55.062000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>GadielHdz</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1856302</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I am creating an extension to test extensibility in the SAP B1 Web Client, but it is not appearing.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;To make sure the issue isn't related to the extension I created, I followed these steps:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;I downloaded the sample file from the documentation to add it directly in the Extension Manager.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_BUSINESS_ONE_WEB_CLIENT/e6ac71d18c7543828bd4463f77d67ff7/5f14e26d0e064d6d89c39b61bca68a6d.html?version=10.0_FP_2305&amp;amp;locale=en-US" target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP Documentation - Adding Extensions&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;I extracted the ZIP file and imported it into the Extension Manager.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GadielHdz_0-1742841303905.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/241890i46895ED0A92E5926/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GadielHdz_0-1742841303905.png" alt="GadielHdz_0-1742841303905.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GadielHdz_1-1742841349081.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/241891iDB3FD40723CA95DB/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GadielHdz_1-1742841349081.png" alt="GadielHdz_1-1742841349081.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;I assigned it to the company.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GadielHdz_2-1742841377507.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/241892iBC9DF7EC2DF4FBA3/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GadielHdz_2-1742841377507.png" alt="GadielHdz_2-1742841377507.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;I opened the Web Client, but the extension does not appear in the corresponding section.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GadielHdz_3-1742841644065.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/241893iBBC5F4BE90D5B727/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GadielHdz_3-1742841644065.png" alt="GadielHdz_3-1742841644065.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;I also checked the side menu, and it is not listed there either.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GadielHdz_4-1742842020755.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/241894i1458ACF78398AC39/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GadielHdz_4-1742842020755.png" alt="GadielHdz_4-1742842020755.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;Am I missing any steps or configurations to make the extension visible?&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":thinking_face:"&gt;🤔&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+Business+One/pd-p/01200615320800000816" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="455-1"&gt;SAP Business One&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+Business+One+Extensibility/pd-p/37d7341b-a1cf-461e-9e60-47ede025c729" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1043-1"&gt;SAP Business One Extensibility&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/sap-b1-web-client-extension-not-showing/qaq-p/14055123"/>
    <published>2025-03-24T19:50:55.062000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
