    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello, I processed a manual journal entry that does not require tax. The processed journal entry appears in the tax report. What could be the reason?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="upextech_0-1742915397346.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/242268iA6004D810C871F6F/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="upextech_0-1742915397346.png" alt="upextech_0-1742915397346.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="upextech_1-1742915411949.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/242269iD2BE633E79601F64/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="upextech_1-1742915411949.png" alt="upextech_1-1742915411949.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
